Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:10.99,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:19.20,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:31.51,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:39.79,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and the other Black Bulls headed \Nto the beach town of Raquey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.79,0:00:43.34,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,in order to go to the Underwater Temple \Nthat lay deep beneath the water there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:47.81,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and the other Black \NBulls received an order
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:49.76,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,to retrieve the magic stone in the temple
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.76,0:00:52.21,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,so they can stop the Eye of the Midnight Sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:57.00,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,who want to separate from the \NClover Kingdom and create their own country.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:00:57.95,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:03.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you all playing around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:05.25,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And you're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:06.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain Yami...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:11.38,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right, gather round, you idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:16.13,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently the Underwater Temple\Nreally is at the bottom of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:20.26,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But the mana kicks up the \Nocean currents so much that,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:23.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,ordinarily, even a first-class \Nmage can't get near it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:26.39,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But on the night of the full moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:29.11,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,the mana becomes weaker.\NWe might be able to get in then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.80,0:01:33.52,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Like the name suggests, the Underwater \NTemple is on the ocean floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:35.37,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just walk to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:37.59,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So Noelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:39.87,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Take us there with your water magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:41.83,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Give us a ride there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:47.33,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I'd need incredible magic \Ncontrol in order to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:48.96,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:50.52,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.16,0:01:53.17,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The next full moon is a week away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.97,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Learn to control it by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:57.93,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Surpass your limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:33.71,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,480)}The Water Girl Grows Up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.86,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:43.89,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just thought I'd let in some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:45.95,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.32,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,What's your foot doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:49.95,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now, how did that get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:52.04,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,This foot is so rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:55.06,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,You were planning to forget your work \Nand go out to play, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:58.47,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,What? Now, why would I go out to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:04:00.36,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to go observe some magic—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:02.89,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:05.08,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Please do your work for once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:06.74,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and shut that window!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:07.62,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:13.98,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... We haven't even resolved the \Nincident with the Eye of the Midnight Sun yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:16.18,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so angry, Marx.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:17.59,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna die young.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:19.07,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,And whose fault is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:21.17,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of the Midnight Sun, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:23.94,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Yami and the others are doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:27.24,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope they aren't fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:30.79,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could've gone to \Nthe Underwater Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:39.46,top,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sick from drinking too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:40.65,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the sun that'll make you shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:44.15,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! How dare you eat my pudding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.55,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,It was yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:48.90,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote my name on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:51.60,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Other people's food always tastes better!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:54.10,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:56.60,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight, my angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.57,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy, munchy, munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:01.28,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Seconds, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:05.78,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off, you assholes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:09.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We're not here to play!\NI can't concentrate like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:10.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:12.29,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:31.96,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful voice.\NI wonder if she's from Raquey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:34.79,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful and ethereal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:37.12,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Are these bubbles magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:40.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, is she a water spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:44.97,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Eek! You heard that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:46.18,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,How embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:48.05,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:48.61,italicstop,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. She's not like what I'd imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:53.06,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now that you've heard me, \Nthere's no way around it. Let's be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.56,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,La-dee-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:57.06,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:01.06,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kahono. What are your names?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:04.88,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Noelle. The meathead is Stupidsta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:07.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling \N"Stupidsta the meathead"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:11.07,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so Noelle and Stupidsta the meathead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:12.61,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,What a strange name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:14.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't believe her! \NHow naïve are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:15.47,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:17.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's totally a nickname, \Nand she's making fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:19.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's Asta! My name's Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:21.58,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Nice to meet you, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:24.46,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,So what were you doing out here, Kahono?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.81,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I was singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.17,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, I could see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.76,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I was doing vocal training.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:32.74,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I love singing at this spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:34.09,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Training?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:37.10,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! I have a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.73,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be a singing,\Ndancing, magic-using...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.40,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:44.95,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What's an idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:46.40,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.01,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:49.19,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:54.10,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,They're all the rage in the Common Realm\Nand Noble Realm right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:55.40,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:58.49,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see... So, you see... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:02.89,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Idols are popular people who \Ncan sing, dance, and use magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:04.01,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:08.59,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become a famous \Nidol and get super rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:10.68,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,So you're after money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:12.76,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What's so great about money, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.63,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,If you do have it, it's just in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:17.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's not in the way! Money's important!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:20.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You've never had to worry about not \Nhaving money, so you wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:22.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But money's really important!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:25.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You can't eat tatoes without any money!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:28.69,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have any tatoes, \Nwhy don't you just eat steak?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:31.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damned royalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:34.28,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Money's really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:36.53,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I totally understand what Stupidsta's saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:38.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, who are you calling "Stupidsta"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:39.68,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Was it Kasta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:41.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it's Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:44.37,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. As—Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:47.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.79,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Stupidsta, your body's weakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:52.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's Asta, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:53.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:53.86,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:56.17,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Your muscles are pretty fatigued.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:08:59.30,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Do you ache when you move?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, how can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:03.89,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,That's my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.25,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Power?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:07.10,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. You'll feel better in a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:11.11,italics,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Song Recovery Magic: Healing Lullaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:16.61,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:22.12,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,She pinpointed each individual spot.\NWhat precise magic use.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:25.51,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,H-How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:34.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is awesome! I don't \Nhurt anywhere anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My body feels so light!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My muscles aren't fatigued anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:41.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kahono! You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:45.24,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen song recovery magic before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:47.73,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.87,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that'll be 100 yuls per session.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:51.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're charging me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:52.65,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:55.63,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:56.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're really charging me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.07,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Money's important, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:00.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.33,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:02.52,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you kindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:05.09,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me know when you \Nwant me to sing for you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:07.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My hundred yuls...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:09.21,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's just spare change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:10.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How is that spare change?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:12.40,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can buy at least ten tatoes with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.84,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,See? It is change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:16.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damned royalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:19.67,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,You're both really funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:21.09,main,kahono,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:22.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:23.10,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:25.26,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'm fifteen, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:26.10,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,We're the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:27.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:29.94,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:33.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, count me in. You're pretty funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:36.72,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A girl my age... who's a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:37.93,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:41.93,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, if you insist, \NI guess I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:44.09,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm willing to be your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:45.83,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.83,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. I'm so happy, I couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:50.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:04.13,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you're both Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:05.33,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:07.22,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:10.62,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's to be expected for me. I'm royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:12.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a peasant, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:16.69,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,So, what brings you to Raquey?\NTaking a vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:19.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're on an important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:21.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're actually trying to get \Nto the Underwater Tem—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:21.28,top,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Stupidsta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:23.38,main,kahono,0000,0000,0000,,The Underwater Temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:25.45,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but this mission's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:27.32,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:30.66,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,So, what were you two up to at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:33.67,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:36.42,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talking about? Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:39.38,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,The moonlight is so romantic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:42.83,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the splashing waves \Nalso heightens the mood and... Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:45.09,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:48.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I was training, too! Magic training!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.48,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Magic training?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:52.79,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah. I can't give you the details,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:58.02,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,but I need to learn how to control my magic \Nwithin the week before the next full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:01.90,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, this important mission—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:03.21,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:07.11,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,So you want to control your magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:10.01,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Noelle. Show me your magic real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:11.05,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:25.11,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:35.35,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Good work, Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:38.58,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we're friends,\NI have some advice for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:39.38,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:40.93,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're trying to hold in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:43.86,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,your mana too much when \Nyou try to control your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.11,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:48.21,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Listen closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:52.59,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:56.65,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I listen to the sound of \Nthe waves to calm myself
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:59.63,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,so I can use my magic exactly how I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:01.63,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly how you want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:08.60,main,Kahno,0000,0000,0000,,It might just be me, but I think that true \Nconcentration comes from a calm heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.63,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,From a calm heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:12.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:17.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I also feel like my best swings happen when \NI'm not thinking about anything at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:18.73,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Would you shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:21.98,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even use magic, and you're \Nnever thinking about anything, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:26.24,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,What's the kindest memory you have \Nthat brings you the most peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:29.21,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,My kindest... memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:31.74,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Maybe your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:33.86,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,My family...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:45.51,flashback,Noelle's dad,0000,0000,0000,,To think that the last thing the \None they called the Steel Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:48.95,flashback,Noelle's dad,0000,0000,0000,,gave this world would be\Nsomeone as useless as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:55.52,flashback,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never accept a failure \Nlike you as family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:57.53,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Solid...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:01.30,flashback,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seriously Mother's child?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:04.78,flashback,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,The House of Silva doesn't \Nneed someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:08.03,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Nebra...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:11.78,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Nozel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:18.25,flashback,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Mother have to die to \Ngive birth to someone like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:28.52,flashbackitalics,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,You killed our mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:34.43,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the advice, Kahono. \NI'll try practicing a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.47,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know if you get tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:41.25,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,It'll only be a hundred... No, it'll only \Nbe a thousand yuls, since you're a royal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:45.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A kind memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:48.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, how are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.66,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You're shining under my sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:55.73,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:03.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:05.50,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:12.70,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You're truly a goddess. \NMy little sister, Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:13.72,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:16.14,main,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Are they having some kind of contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:22.74,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:28.17,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kahono.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:30.99,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,You can just pay me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:32.20,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.06,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:42.50,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't drink any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:48.02,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:50.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:16:01.52,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone left me... \NWon't someone come get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:14.49,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The full moon is tomorrow... \NTonight's my last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:17.91,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! You've almost got it, Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:22.33,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time... I still \Ncan't control it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.67,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the mission will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:27.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:28.55,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:33.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle! Stop thinking,\Nand set all of your magic free!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:34.36,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:35.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:40.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That thing from the first time you lost control \Nwould probably go underwater the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:46.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what Kahono said earlier? \NThat you were holding your magic back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:50.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, maybe it'll work \Nif you just let everything loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:52.55,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:53.53,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't work—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:56.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I told you! If that happens, \NI'll use my sword to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:59.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry and just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:04.96,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! Don't blame me if something happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:11.71,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm releasing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.21,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,all my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:20.72,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:29.73,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! This isn't going to work at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:33.33,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to relax in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:39.69,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:41.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:46.72,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I really can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:47.80,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:53.64,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any... kind memories at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:56.90,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:59.89,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:02.68,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You're always talking big, \Nso what the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:05.56,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself a Black Bull?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:08.26,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,All that awesome magic is going to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:11.59,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and learn how to control it\Nso you can fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:15.47,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine! Even if you mess up,\Nyou won't die or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:16.82,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Just take it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:18.97,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:21.57,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and finish so you can eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:25.20,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you fall, I'll catch you gently!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:28.33,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,If you fall, I'm kicking you back \Nup there, so make this work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:31.33,sign_26574_299_Grey_Disguised_a,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Grey Disguised as Magna
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:31.33,top,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Just get it done, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle! You can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.13,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I had some...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:47.03,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Some kind memories within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:52.36,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Nozel's little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:58.85,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Your big bro mentioned that you're some \Nloser who can't even control her magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:02.13,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And that you wouldn't be able to pass \Nthe Entrance Exam even if you tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:06.12,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a royal fail before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:07.87,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:12.13,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you feel like fighting, \Nwhy don't you come join my team?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.22,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:17.43,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The absolute worst Magic \NKnights squad, the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:19.63,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We're all nothing but losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:22.05,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning we're perfect for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:29.11,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I was with my family for years, but I didn't \Nhave a single pleasant memory of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:34.40,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's only been a few months since \NI joined the Black Bulls, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:38.40,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I have so many memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.28,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,So many kind memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.12,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:52.34,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,They all acknowledged me \Nand gave me a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:56.59,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:04.30,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea Dragon's Cradle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:14.06,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I... I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:16.06,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:19.07,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The Sea Dragon's Cradle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:22.04,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! I really did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:27.77,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get distracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:29.66,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:34.33,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This feels great after \Nbeing in the sun all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:39.51,main,Final,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:40.55,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:44.80,main,Final,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! That was my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:47.54,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stupidsta...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:49.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.05,0:20:52.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.69,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Could you not touch me so casually?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:57.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:20:59.32,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:02.04,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness everything ended well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:03.57,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:05.89,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Kahono! I did it—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:08.25,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Kahono?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:10.88,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Time to celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:12.33,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.69,0:21:14.57,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:21.91,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Noelle.\NYou surpassed your limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:24.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, guess we should get going
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:26.57,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,to the Underwater Temple.
